<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1290302-is-this-based-off-firestarter-by-stephen">Is this based off Firestarter by Stephen King? In King&#39;s book Charlene &quot;Charlie&quot; McGee a child of two parents who were part of a scientific study had a special power where she can start fires.

I really enjoyed King&#39;s book so if anyone has read both if also like to know how they compare.</a>
</div>
