<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/19522680-lolita-mcmillan">Lolita Mcmillan</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I read both Firestarter and Bone Music. I enjoyed both of them. In my opinion they are both great books, I don&apos;t think Bone Music was based on Mr. Kin<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I read both Firestarter and Bone Music. I enjoyed both of them. In my opinion they are both great books, I don't think Bone Music was based on Mr. King's book. Charlotte, in Bone Music is a wonderful character. She took what life threw at her and dealt with it. I like a strong woman character. This book kept my attention from the first page to the end. I will be reading more from Christopher Rice.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
