<span id="freeTextContainer17194903239938033053">I suspected Christopher Rice was a successful author riding on his mother&apos;s (Anne Rice) coattails, but this turned out to be a first rate thriller, and I apologize to him for my unworthy expectations!</span>
  <span id="freeText17194903239938033053" style="display:none">I suspected Christopher Rice was a successful author riding on his mother's (Anne Rice) coattails, but this turned out to be a first rate thriller, and I apologize to him for my unworthy expectations!</span>
